Pod-Elemental-MakeSelector version 0.01, released July 14, 2012


This module provides an alternative to Pod::Elemental::Selectors.  It
allows more complex criteria to be expressed by a single selector,
including criteria that Pod::Elemental::Selectors doesn't currently
handle.



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install



DEPENDENCIES

  Package        Minimum Version
  -------------- ---------------
  perl            5.010
  Carp            
  Sub::Exporter



CHANGES
    Here's what's new in version 0.01 of Pod-Elemental-MakeSelector:
